article_title: Rubio Defunded Obamacare While Cruz And Trump Blustered

article_metadata.description: What is Senator Marco Rubio's greatest Senate accomplishment? It may turn out to be a very smart and savvy defunding of Obamacare and a prevention of a taxpayer bailout of Big Insurance.
article_metadata.author: Ryan Ellis
